data.description: Welcome to your dream home! Seller is motivated. This remodeled 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom house is a true gem, boasting great curb appeal and an ideal layout for entertaining. VERY family oriented neighborhood! NO HOA  Step inside to discover the elegant 32" marble tile floors.  The kitchen features quartz countertops, recessed lighting, and not one but two refrigerators.  The backyard is inviting with the oval-shaped above-ground pool, surrounded by a beautifully crafted wooden deck.  The impact windows and doors not only enhance the property's aesthetics but also provide added security and energy efficiency.  Parking will never be an issue with the ample space available on the stamped concrete driveway. Additionally, the expansive backyard offers endless possibilities for outdoor activities. Welcome to your dream home! This recently remodeled 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom house is a true gem, boasting great curb appeal and an ideal layout for entertaining.
